meta.title: Market Psychology Map: Semantic News Clusters

inspector.description: Uses OpenAI Embeddings + t-SNE (Dimensionality Reduction) to map 1,536 dimensions of news context into 2D space. Bubbles are colored by Market Impact (Bull Trap vs Justified Optimism).
inspector.sql_logic:
SELECT 
    news_id,
    ticker,
    title,
    published_at,
    x,
    y,
    cluster_id,
    sentiment,
    impact,
    label
FROM STOCKS_ELT_DB.MARTS.MARTS_MASSIVE__NEWS_CLUSTERS
WHERE x IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY published_at DESC
LIMIT 2000
inspector.dbt_logic:
-- 1. PYTHON CALCULATION LAYER (models/intermediate/int_massive__news_clusters.py)
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from sklearn.manifold import TSNE
from sklearn.cluster import KMeans

def model(dbt, session):
    dbt.config(packages = ["pandas", "scikit-learn", "numpy"])
    
    # Load vectors
    df = dbt.ref("int_massive__news_cluster_prep").to_pandas()
    matrix = np.stack(df['SUMMARY_EMBEDDING'].values)

    # Run t-SNE (1536 dims -> 2 dims)
    tsne = TSNE(n_components=2, perplexity=30, random_state=42)
    projections = tsne.fit_transform(matrix)

    # Run K-Means (Topic Detection)
    kmeans = KMeans(n_clusters=8, random_state=42)
    clusters = kmeans.fit_predict(matrix)

    df['X_COORD'] = projections[:, 0]
    df['Y_COORD'] = projections[:, 1]
    df['CLUSTER_ID'] = clusters
    return df

-- 2. MART INTERFACE (models/marts/massive/marts_massive__news_clusters.sql)
SELECT 
    news_id,
    ticker,
    title,
    published_at,
    X_COORD as x,
    Y_COORD as y,
    CLUSTER_ID as cluster_id,
    sentiment_score as sentiment,
    market_impact_pct as impact,
    narrative_label as label
FROM {{ ref('int_massive__news_clusters') }}
inspector.dbt_yml:
- name: int_massive__news_clusters
    description: >
      [PYTHON MODEL]: Feeds the 'Semantic Cluster Map'.
      Uses Snowpark (t-SNE) to reduce 1536-dim embeddings to 2D coordinates.
    tags: ["dashboard", "ai", "python", "massive"]

  - name: marts_massive__news_clusters
    description: >
      [VIEW]: The Public API for the Market Psychology Map.
      Reads calculated coordinates from the intermediate Python layer and formats them for the frontend.
    tags: ["dashboard", "marts", "ai"]
